
Web Infrastructure: Single-Server Setup
Overview
This project documents a basic web infrastructure designed to host a website reachable via www.foobar.com. The setup utilizes a single-server architecture commonly referred to as a LAMP (Linux, Apache/Nginx, MySQL, PHP/Python/etc.) stack.
